title: Bodybuilding - The Islander Johnny Doull 2014
description: Johnny Doull is a young rising star in the bodybuilding world. He's unique for a lot of reasons, one of which being that he lives in Prince Edward Island- definitely not a bodybuilding hotspot. Can his relentless drive to succeed take him to the top of this often mis-understood sport? It better, as he has no Plan-B. It's all or nothing, and for Johnny, bodybuilding is everything
